reviews.review_text:
not bad... Hats off to you, Joe! The recording quality here is very good.  There appears to be some extremely minor distortion in the recording, but otherwise great.  Joe has been uploading a bunch of shows that there were previously only crummy recordings of.  Thanks again!
This show is a decent one.  I have fond memories of my bringing my mother and father to the show.  The Playing in the Band is an overlooked gem as far as I'm concerned.  The rest is also good.
